Usage: set_annotated_transition [-help] <slew_value> <port_or_pin_list> [-fall]
                                [-max] [-min] [-rise]

-help                     # Prints out the command usage
<slew_value>              # Transition time to be annotated to the selected
                          # pins or ports (float, required)
<port_or_pin_list>        # List of pins or ports to be annotated with the
                          # transition time that you specify using the
                          # slew_value parameter (string, required)
-fall                     # Transition value is set for falling transition time
                          # (bool, optional)
-max                      # Transition value is set for maximum transition time
                          # (bool, optional)
-min                      # Transition value is set for minimum transition time
                          # (bool, optional)
-rise                     # Transition value is set for rising transition time
                          # (bool, optional)